{
  "stem": "27340.2",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "But they didn't parade.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "They didn't parade.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And they wanted to keep themselves as far away from any paramilitarism or any military discipline that the Nazis were so fond of, a-a-as, as, as possible.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So yes, I, I, I, I had this feeling as a young boy, what a pity I couldn't get into this.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And had I grown up a normal life here in England, let us assume if I would have been born here in England, then I dare say I would have joined the Boy Scouts and then later on most probably the Cadet Force.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That was, you know [LAUGHS], a sort of driving force, as it were.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So there was a conflict about being a fairly studious though active Jewish boy?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Oh, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That was always impressive.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I daresay, if you see some of the pictures of, uh, the way they paraded with their flags and with their symbols and so on, I, I, I'm impressed by this, in the same way as I'm impressed by the, uh, the, the, the trooping of the colors, for instance, here in London.",
      "word_count": 54
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "This is an impressive military display I'm, I'm very fond of.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, I suppose so.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In the back of my mind, I knew these people.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And some of them were people with whom I went to school in the earlier stages were amongst those who were beating me up.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But, uh, since I never suffered a broken leg or often came home with a bleeding nose or perhaps a scratch or two on my legs or so, I didn't, it didn't demure me all that much from retaining that little bit of respect for that sort of pompous militarism.",
      "word_count": 50
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[SIGHS] Maybe I did.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't remember that.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
